HEADWORD: Actually
<hw>Ac"tu*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Actively.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Neither <xex>actually</xex> . . . nor
